ine and notice how it warms your skin.<\/li><li>Light a candle and watch the flame dance.&#8221;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-2-quotes-from-others\">2 QUOTES FROM OTHERS<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>I.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fantasy writer <strong>J.R.R. Tolkien<\/strong> on being overlooked:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;Deeds will not be less valiant because they are unpraised.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: As said by Aragorn in <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Return-King-Lord-Rings\/dp\/0618002243\">\u200b<em>The Return of the King<\/em>\u200b<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200bII.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Novelist <strong>Chuck Palahniuk<\/strong> on memory:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;It&#8217;s so hard to forget pain, but it&#8217;s even harder to remember sweetness. We have no scar to show for happiness. We learn so little from peace.&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Source: <\/em><a href=\"https:\/\/amzn.to\/4b1QiW4\">\u200b<em>Diary<\/em><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-1-question-for-you\">1 QUESTION FOR YOU<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Make a list of the people in your field who enjoy unfair advantages. How can you collaborate with them?<\/p>\n\n\n<div id=\"block_a7318619c6503c8b765bfb7b5133813d\" class=\"twitter-share \" data-easygut-id=\"twitter\">\n\t<div><a href=\"https:\/\/ctt.ac\/4XYQU\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"27\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 27\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\">\n<circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"14\" r=\"12\" fill=\"#EDEADE\"\/>\n<path d=\"M16.3613 12.1406C16.791 11.8184 17.1777 11.4316 17.4785 10.9805C17.0918 11.1523 16.6406 11.2812 16.1895 11.3242C16.6621 11.0449 17.0059 10.6152 17.1777 10.0781C16.748 10.3359 16.2539 10.5293 15.7598 10.6367C15.3301 10.1855 14.75 9.92773 14.1055 9.92773C12.8594 9.92773 11.8496 10.9375 11.8496 12.1836C11.8496 12.3555 11.8711 12.5273 11.9141 12.6992C10.0449 12.5918 8.36914 11.6895 7.25195 10.3359C7.05859 10.6582 6.95117 11.0449 6.95117 11.4746C6.95117 12.248 7.33789 12.9355 7.96094 13.3438C7.5957 13.3223 7.23047 13.2363 6.92969 13.0645V13.0859C6.92969 14.